description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Bodyweight Strength' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Groove Session and The Nightclub Workout vibe.
The The Groove Session vibe means Fun, fluid, expressive, completely in the moment. This is especially good for Days when you want to move intuitively and just vibe. The The Nightclub Workout vibe means Lights down, music up, full-body euphoria. This is especially good for When you want to move like no oneâ€™s watching and feel amazing..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Get your heart pumping with Pete as you move from one lower body exercise to another at the enchanting Bardini Garden in Florence. Yoga blocks optional....
